title: When I Met REAL 'INDIANS' of CUBA
description:
During my Cuba trip, I visited Vinales and Varadero from Havana. I met someone from Cuba's indigenous community who had resided there before the arrival of the Spanish from Europe. This marks the final instalment of the Cuban series.  #MountainTrekker #Cuba #travelvlog
